{
  "stem": "23438.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Rarely as a family together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My parents rarely went out together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mother had her circle of friends, her bridge.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Father had his goings out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We never knew where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think I was a jealous little bitch, at the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was more able, at school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was learning quicker than him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I was really quite-- well, he was very gentle with me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He felt he was older, and a lot stronger.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he felt he had to protect me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was really, very often, quite nasty.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I would scratch and kick, and do all that, whatever little bitches do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He was-- we both were-- learning to play the piano with Uncle Jozef, who was a bit of a piano teacher.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I was-- I wasn't making much of a progress, whereas my brother was very good at it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] He was 14 when the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was 12.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was a very big boy, then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was tall, well built.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He looked a lot older than that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You could give him 18.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's how I remember him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never seen him afterwards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You said before, that you had-- and your family, there was no religion.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But were you aware of any anti-Semitism--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, I was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were times when-- I did not meet it at school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Neither in the first elementary school, nor in the French school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it had happened a number of times that in the street, I was walking to a lesson, or wherever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A man had stopped me and said, [FRENCH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Go back where you came from.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I would then run home, crying, to mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
